1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,640
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,270
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:41,791 --> 00:00:42,416
Coming.

4
00:00:46,875 --> 00:00:49,583
Chief Squad Leader Cheng Xintian
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau

5
00:00:49,916 --> 00:00:50,750
greets the Young Duke.

6
00:00:58,375 --> 00:00:59,250
You know it?

7
00:01:04,791 --> 00:01:05,666
Bingfan knows too.

8
00:01:09,583 --> 00:01:10,333
Leave us.

9
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:10,916
Yes.

10
00:01:19,416 --> 00:01:19,958
Bingfan.

11
00:01:23,791 --> 00:01:25,541
Baihu Shen Bingfan
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau

12
00:01:25,541 --> 00:01:26,250
greets the Young Duke.

13
00:01:28,541 --> 00:01:29,041
Bingfan.

14
00:01:31,041 --> 00:01:32,000
Please let me explain.

15
00:01:33,833 --> 00:01:35,458
I didn't know who you were before.

16
00:01:35,625 --> 00:01:36,208
Forgive my offense.

17
00:01:36,375 --> 00:01:37,166
It will not happen again.

18
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:42,810
♪In a fleeting moment♪

19
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,583
Bingfan.

20
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:44,958
Bingfan.

21
00:01:45,750 --> 00:01:47,000
I knew once my identity came out,

22
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,791
this would happen.

23
00:01:48,041 --> 00:01:49,541
But I truly was not lying to you,
Bingfan.

24
00:01:49,958 --> 00:01:50,833
Please hear me out.

25
00:01:52,916 --> 00:01:54,833
You may think I had
some hidden agenda.

26
00:01:55,125 --> 00:01:56,833
You may think I was playing with you.

27
00:01:56,833 --> 00:01:57,958
But I swear I was not.

28
00:01:58,250 --> 00:01:59,916
I never wanted to be some Young Duke.

29
00:02:00,291 --> 00:02:02,708
I like living free.

30
00:02:02,958 --> 00:02:04,625
The heirship was never meant to be mine.

31
00:02:04,875 --> 00:02:06,458
It only fell to me

32
00:02:06,458 --> 00:02:07,666
after my brother was injured
and disabled.

33
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:10,458
I don't want to become Duke Zheng.

34
00:02:11,041 --> 00:02:12,583
I only want to run Chong'er Pavilion.

35
00:02:15,541 --> 00:02:16,541
I truly didn't mean to hide it.

36
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,833
I only kept my identity from you.

37
00:02:18,541 --> 00:02:19,625
I never meant to deceive you.

38
00:02:20,833 --> 00:02:21,541
Chang Beiming.

39
00:02:21,958 --> 00:02:23,208
Do I look like a three-year-old?

40
00:02:24,083 --> 00:02:26,000
No. I mean it.

41
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:29,500
I hate the life of noble houses.

42
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,916
I just want to live freely.

43
00:02:31,166 --> 00:02:32,666
When I said I wanted to sail south
with you

44
00:02:32,958 --> 00:02:34,541
and roam the martial world together,
I meant it.

45
00:02:34,958 --> 00:02:35,625
And when I said

46
00:02:35,833 --> 00:02:37,541
I would help you catch Leng Xin
and avenge your father,

47
00:02:38,083 --> 00:02:39,041
every word came from my heart.

48
00:02:40,583 --> 00:02:41,583
Aside from my identity,

49
00:02:42,333 --> 00:02:43,791
I never lied to you
about anything else.

50
00:02:44,875 --> 00:02:46,750
Then why did you never say
you knew Princess Pingyang?

51
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,791
You even pretended not to know
during our meeting.

52
00:02:50,333 --> 00:02:52,708
Chang Beiming, how much
are you hiding?

53
00:02:52,833 --> 00:02:53,250
Listen.

54
00:02:54,250 --> 00:02:56,375
It is true
that I know Princess Pingyang.

55
00:02:56,375 --> 00:02:57,833
It is also true
that I can't stand her.

56
00:02:58,416 --> 00:02:59,625
She is spoiled and affected.

57
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:02,791
How could she compare
to your courage and spirit?

58
00:03:03,875 --> 00:03:05,083
And that engagement she mentioned.

59
00:03:05,166 --> 00:03:06,541
That was drunken talk
between the elders.

60
00:03:06,541 --> 00:03:07,333
It does not count.

61
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,541
I will never accept it.

62
00:03:10,958 --> 00:03:12,083
I have known her since childhood.

63
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:13,416
If I liked her,

64
00:03:13,916 --> 00:03:15,083
I would have liked her long ago.

65
00:03:17,916 --> 00:03:19,208
Childhood sweethearts, then.

66
00:03:20,291 --> 00:03:20,458
Bingfan.

67
00:03:20,666 --> 00:03:21,333
No.

68
00:03:23,083 --> 00:03:23,375
Not like that.

69
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,041
That is not what I meant.

70
00:03:25,166 --> 00:03:26,625
What childhood sweethearts?

71
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,083
Nonsense.

72
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,625
Chang Beiming.

73
00:03:30,541 --> 00:03:32,083
You look shameless
when you make excuses.

74
00:03:32,958 --> 00:03:33,708
Come on.

75
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:39,640
(Leisurely and Free)

76
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,100
(Leisurely and Free)

77
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,958
I knew his background was not simple.

78
00:04:01,583 --> 00:04:04,250
I didn't expect it
to be that powerful.

79
00:04:05,875 --> 00:04:06,750
Hua.

80
00:04:07,208 --> 00:04:09,916
Isn't it good that Young Master Chang
has a powerful background?

81
00:04:10,291 --> 00:04:11,583
He is still Young Master Chang.

82
00:04:12,083 --> 00:04:12,916
What do you know?

83
00:04:13,458 --> 00:04:15,625
With a status like his,
what about Bingfan?

84
00:04:16,375 --> 00:04:17,041
What does that have to do with me?

85
00:04:20,291 --> 00:04:22,666
Even a blind man can see he likes you.

86
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:26,208
I... I can see it too.

87
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:30,750
But if Young Master Chang
likes Bingfan,

88
00:04:31,083 --> 00:04:33,041
why not just let him marry you?

89
00:04:37,708 --> 00:04:38,750
With Bingfan's status,

90
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:41,791
even if Young Master Chang
wants to marry her,

91
00:04:42,541 --> 00:04:43,958
what about his family?

92
00:04:44,166 --> 00:04:45,666
They would never agree.

93
00:04:45,958 --> 00:04:47,458
Even if he wants to, I don't.

94
00:04:48,583 --> 00:04:49,583
Then why are you so angry?

95
00:04:49,875 --> 00:04:51,041
Angry enough to drink here?

96
00:04:52,416 --> 00:04:53,750
Because I hate being lied to.

97
00:04:55,083 --> 00:04:56,791
What did he lie about?

98
00:04:56,916 --> 00:04:59,250
His Chong'er Pavilion identity
is real.

99
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,416
He simply didn't tell you

100
00:05:01,416 --> 00:05:02,666
about his other identity.

101
00:05:03,083 --> 00:05:05,041
That is not exactly lying.

102
00:05:09,958 --> 00:05:11,208
Honestly,

103
00:05:12,333 --> 00:05:14,291
hiding the truth is still lying.

104
00:05:16,083 --> 00:05:17,416
Whose side are you on?

105
00:05:17,625 --> 00:05:19,541
Bingfan, of course.

106
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:21,916
You sweet little fool.

107
00:05:23,583 --> 00:05:25,833
Bingfan, if you think
Young Master Chang is no good,

108
00:05:26,125 --> 00:05:28,208
then don't choose him.

109
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,875
Choose Guan Yunfeng.

110
00:05:30,291 --> 00:05:31,625
He treats you well, too.

111
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:35,166
Enough, both of you.

112
00:05:36,083 --> 00:05:37,000
I told you long ago.

113
00:05:37,541 --> 00:05:39,041
Love and romance mean nothing to me.

114
00:05:40,583 --> 00:05:42,291
My priority is to catch Leng Xin.

115
00:05:42,916 --> 00:05:44,833
I will not choose Chang Beiming
or Guan Yunfeng.

116
00:05:45,041 --> 00:05:46,333
I only want to avenge my father.

117
00:05:47,666 --> 00:05:48,833
Until that is done,

118
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,541
I will not think about any of this.

119
00:06:06,125 --> 00:06:07,166
Off to work, ladies?

120
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:09,375
Breakfast is ready. Have some.

121
00:06:10,416 --> 00:06:11,458
No need to trouble yourself,
Young Duke.

122
00:06:11,625 --> 00:06:12,458
The Northern Bureau has breakfast.

123
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:18,166
She is angry. Please bear with her,
Young Duke.

124
00:06:22,625 --> 00:06:23,333
I will let it slide for your sake.

125
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:25,458
Who asked you to?

126
00:06:30,416 --> 00:06:30,833
She really left.

127
00:06:31,458 --> 00:06:32,375
Poor Young Master.

128
00:06:32,958 --> 00:06:33,708
Chang Huan. Chang Le.

129
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,375
Yes.

130
00:06:37,125 --> 00:06:38,583
From now on,

131
00:06:39,208 --> 00:06:42,375
Princess Pingyang is not allowed
one step into Chong'er Pavilion.

132
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,166
But...

133
00:06:43,625 --> 00:06:45,625
Young Master, she is a princess.

134
00:06:45,958 --> 00:06:47,791
If she comes, we cannot stop her.

135
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:48,625
Figure it out yourselves.

136
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,250
Young Master, is it good?

137
00:06:57,625 --> 00:06:58,791
My cooking is not bad, is it?

138
00:06:58,791 --> 00:06:59,791
I made it!

139
00:07:02,833 --> 00:07:05,333
Young Master, you have been posing
for half an hour.

140
00:07:05,625 --> 00:07:06,875
Why not take a break?

141
00:07:09,791 --> 00:07:10,833
Still not here?

142
00:07:11,083 --> 00:07:11,666
Young Master!

143
00:07:11,916 --> 00:07:12,750
She is here!

144
00:07:14,041 --> 00:07:15,625
Come on. One, two, three. Go.

145
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,666
Bingfan.

146
00:07:28,083 --> 00:07:29,083
The mung bean soup is ready.

147
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,833
Perfect timing.

148
00:07:34,833 --> 00:07:35,333
Bingfan.

149
00:07:38,458 --> 00:07:40,833
Bingfan, just have one sip.

150
00:07:47,916 --> 00:07:49,083
With poses that ugly,

151
00:07:49,916 --> 00:07:51,250
will Bingfan even look at me?

152
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:52,458
But

153
00:07:53,333 --> 00:07:54,291
it was his fault.

154
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,125
Keep practicing.

155
00:07:55,791 --> 00:07:57,125
I thought I looked pretty good.

156
00:07:57,625 --> 00:07:58,583
Keep practicing!

157
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:06,875
(First-Rank Lady of Duke Zheng's Manor)
I have laid my heart bare.

158
00:08:07,375 --> 00:08:08,375
Please stand by me, Mother.

159
00:08:08,625 --> 00:08:09,625
So,

160
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:12,416
you won't marry the princess.

161
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:14,000
Back then,

162
00:08:14,416 --> 00:08:15,750
when I agreed to take

163
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,416
my brother's place
as Duke Zheng's heir,

164
00:08:18,041 --> 00:08:18,875
we had an agreement.

165
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:21,750
My private affairs were mine
to decide.

166
00:08:22,166 --> 00:08:24,000
You and Father would not interfere.

167
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:26,541
Now my heart is already taken.

168
00:08:27,250 --> 00:08:28,208
So, Mother,

169
00:08:29,958 --> 00:08:30,583
please help me.

170
00:08:31,125 --> 00:08:31,791
I fear

171
00:08:32,458 --> 00:08:34,083
Pingyang will not let this go.

172
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,666
And the Empress Dowager

173
00:08:37,375 --> 00:08:38,583
will expect an answer.

174
00:08:39,291 --> 00:08:40,625
If you step in, Mother,

175
00:08:41,583 --> 00:08:42,333
it should not be hard.

176
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,375
Well...

177
00:08:45,333 --> 00:08:46,833
You have been making trouble
for me since you were little.

178
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:48,666
Very well.

179
00:08:49,791 --> 00:08:51,166
No good comes from forcing a marriage.

180
00:08:51,958 --> 00:08:53,541
You need not marry Princess Pingyang.

181
00:08:53,958 --> 00:08:56,416
But if you wish to bring someone
into this family,

182
00:08:57,458 --> 00:08:59,083
I must approve her first.

183
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:00,208
Of course.

184
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:02,291
Thank you, Mother.

185
00:09:02,916 --> 00:09:03,958
And your brother?

186
00:09:04,625 --> 00:09:05,541
What have you found?

187
00:09:09,416 --> 00:09:10,166
I have a few leads.

188
00:09:11,208 --> 00:09:12,958
Beixiao would not listen to me.

189
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:15,041
He insisted on taking command
of the Northern Bureau.

190
00:09:16,375 --> 00:09:17,250
He had no idea

191
00:09:17,708 --> 00:09:19,666
how dangerous those waters were.

192
00:09:20,375 --> 00:09:22,333
It even drew in the Crown Prince
and Prince Fu.

193
00:09:23,166 --> 00:09:25,000
Even Zhang Weimin,
with all his schemes,

194
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,916
had to take a desperate move
and recruit female Jinyiwei.

195
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:29,625
He wanted to use

196
00:09:29,625 --> 00:09:31,458
these girls with no powerful backing

197
00:09:31,875 --> 00:09:33,083
to muddy the waters

198
00:09:33,416 --> 00:09:34,625
so he could fish in them.

199
00:09:35,375 --> 00:09:37,541
This has become a succession struggle.

200
00:09:38,166 --> 00:09:40,458
Few people could have ambushed
your brother and left him crippled.

201
00:09:41,291 --> 00:09:42,750
It had to be someone

202
00:09:43,625 --> 00:09:44,916
he trusted, or had reason to trust.

203
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:46,458
Back then,

204
00:09:47,583 --> 00:09:49,000
the two men he trusted most

205
00:09:50,458 --> 00:09:51,375
were Zhang Weimin

206
00:09:52,083 --> 00:09:53,416
and Qianhu Shen Lian.

207
00:09:54,625 --> 00:09:55,375
Beixiao

208
00:09:56,666 --> 00:09:58,083
was struck from behind.

209
00:09:58,083 --> 00:09:59,166
He never saw who did it.

210
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,500
So,

211
00:10:02,166 --> 00:10:03,125
look into this carefully.

212
00:10:04,583 --> 00:10:05,875
And protect yourself.

213
00:10:06,875 --> 00:10:07,708
I will, Mother.

214
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:11,500
His Majesty

215
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:14,875
is still waiting for your report.

216
00:10:17,875 --> 00:10:18,916
I know what to do.

217
00:10:29,625 --> 00:10:31,375
Be more careful next time.

218
00:10:31,916 --> 00:10:33,333
If I had not arrived in time...

219
00:10:33,708 --> 00:10:34,333
Got it.

220
00:10:49,375 --> 00:10:50,166
Young Master.

221
00:10:50,583 --> 00:10:51,416
An honored guest is here.

222
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,750
Go back to your room.

223
00:11:01,333 --> 00:11:02,000
You all may leave.

224
00:11:02,416 --> 00:11:02,750
Yes.

225
00:11:08,791 --> 00:11:09,750
Bingfan. Hua.

226
00:11:10,708 --> 00:11:12,208
Is that really His Majesty
in the front courtyard?

227
00:11:12,541 --> 00:11:13,583
Who else could make

228
00:11:13,583 --> 00:11:15,041
Chang Beiming be that respectful

229
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:16,750
except the Emperor himself?

230
00:11:18,208 --> 00:11:18,875
But

231
00:11:19,166 --> 00:11:20,916
His Majesty has not held court
for years.

232
00:11:21,833 --> 00:11:23,333
Why would he come
to Chong'er Pavilion?

233
00:11:26,166 --> 00:11:28,250
If I'm not mistaken,

234
00:11:28,875 --> 00:11:31,416
he is here because
of Princess Pingyang.

235
00:11:36,666 --> 00:11:37,375
What are you doing?

236
00:11:41,083 --> 00:11:41,833
What is Bingfan doing?

237
00:11:42,875 --> 00:11:43,416
Moving out.

238
00:11:44,708 --> 00:11:45,416
Moving out?

239
00:11:47,208 --> 00:11:48,791
Bingfan, why are you moving out?

240
00:11:49,291 --> 00:11:51,083
Better to leave myself
than wait to be thrown out.

241
00:11:53,416 --> 00:11:56,291
You are acting too rashly.

242
00:11:56,458 --> 00:11:59,083
We don't even know
what he said to the Emperor.

243
00:11:59,416 --> 00:12:00,916
The Duke Zheng household

244
00:12:01,333 --> 00:12:03,083
helped found the dynasty.

245
00:12:03,458 --> 00:12:05,916
Even the Emperor has to show them
some respect.

246
00:12:07,958 --> 00:12:09,958
Your Majesty came all the way
to Chong'er Pavilion

247
00:12:10,291 --> 00:12:11,833
because of Princess Pingyang?

248
00:12:12,791 --> 00:12:13,583
My sister

249
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:16,708
wept before my mother.

250
00:12:17,416 --> 00:12:18,791
The Empress Dowager was heartbroken.

251
00:12:19,875 --> 00:12:20,541
So,

252
00:12:21,083 --> 00:12:24,750
I had no choice but to come here
late at night

253
00:12:25,291 --> 00:12:26,375
and ask you myself.

254
00:12:27,291 --> 00:12:28,750
What do you intend to do

255
00:12:29,666 --> 00:12:30,708
about this marriage?

256
00:12:35,625 --> 00:12:36,291
Your Majesty,

257
00:12:37,583 --> 00:12:40,708
I truly don't love Princess Pingyang.

258
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,500
Because your heart belongs to another?

259
00:12:49,041 --> 00:12:49,541
Yes.

260
00:12:52,666 --> 00:12:53,458
If

261
00:12:54,041 --> 00:12:55,625
I issue an edict for this marriage,

262
00:12:56,791 --> 00:12:58,791
would you still defy me?

263
00:13:00,916 --> 00:13:01,416
Your Majesty,

264
00:13:02,541 --> 00:13:04,000
for the sake of the Chang family's
generations of loyalty,

265
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:06,291
please take back the order.
Otherwise...

266
00:13:06,916 --> 00:13:08,041
Otherwise?

267
00:13:11,041 --> 00:13:12,250
If Your Majesty leaves me no choice,

268
00:13:13,458 --> 00:13:16,000
I'll have to use the Iron Certificate,
our family's imperial pardon.

269
00:13:25,541 --> 00:13:27,666
For some lowborn woman,

270
00:13:27,958 --> 00:13:30,541
you would use the Iron Certificate
against me?

271
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,666
Your Majesty,

272
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:33,791
if you force my hand,
what choice do I have?

273
00:13:36,208 --> 00:13:37,666
What kind of woman

274
00:13:38,291 --> 00:13:41,333
could make you go this far?

275
00:13:43,458 --> 00:13:46,375
The only woman I want.

276
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,625
In that case,

277
00:13:53,041 --> 00:13:53,791
all right.

278
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,875
Pingyang simply was not meant
for this match.

279
00:13:59,250 --> 00:14:00,500
Thank you, Your Majesty.

280
00:14:01,125 --> 00:14:02,291
Come on. Get up.

281
00:14:06,791 --> 00:14:08,291
How is the other matter going?

282
00:14:13,458 --> 00:14:14,208
I have leads.

283
00:14:15,208 --> 00:14:16,666
Don't delay my real business.

284
00:14:17,458 --> 00:14:18,208
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

285
00:14:18,791 --> 00:14:19,458
I will get

286
00:14:19,875 --> 00:14:21,833
to the bottom of it.

287
00:14:22,291 --> 00:14:23,458
Well done, Young Master Chang!

288
00:14:24,083 --> 00:14:26,041
He is so devoted!

289
00:14:27,083 --> 00:14:27,666
Bingfan.

290
00:14:28,166 --> 00:14:29,500
Are you happy now?

291
00:14:31,041 --> 00:14:33,000
He never said who the woman was.

292
00:14:34,291 --> 00:14:35,166
Bingfan.

293
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:36,416
Seriously?

294
00:14:36,833 --> 00:14:38,208
Let her pretend.

295
00:14:38,375 --> 00:14:40,583
Inside, she must be glowing.

296
00:14:47,708 --> 00:14:48,166
What are you laughing at?

297
00:14:52,541 --> 00:14:53,208
Young Master Chang.

298
00:14:54,125 --> 00:14:54,708
Not bad.

299
00:14:55,375 --> 00:14:55,791
Not bad at all.

300
00:14:56,458 --> 00:14:57,041
Young Master Chang.

301
00:15:06,250 --> 00:15:06,625
What is it?

302
00:15:08,583 --> 00:15:09,291
His Majesty is gone?

303
00:15:09,583 --> 00:15:11,583
I heard you were moving out?

304
00:15:13,541 --> 00:15:14,750
Who said I was moving out?

305
00:15:16,166 --> 00:15:17,166
His Majesty offered you a marriage.

306
00:15:17,541 --> 00:15:18,291
Why refuse?

307
00:15:18,291 --> 00:15:19,666
I don't like Princess Pingyang.

308
00:15:19,666 --> 00:15:20,416
Then who do you like?

309
00:15:28,770 --> 00:15:29,875
(Northern Bureau)

310
00:15:29,875 --> 00:15:30,833
(Northern Bureau)
A rebellion in the Kingdom of Liao

311
00:15:31,125 --> 00:15:32,083
got the King killed.

312
00:15:32,458 --> 00:15:34,625
The royal clan was slaughtered.

313
00:15:35,583 --> 00:15:37,416
Only the Ninth Prince, Fa Yuanrong,

314
00:15:37,416 --> 00:15:38,791
who was studying
at our Imperial College,

315
00:15:38,958 --> 00:15:39,916
survived.

316
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:41,583
The Cabinet has ordered

317
00:15:41,666 --> 00:15:42,583
the Jinyiwei

318
00:15:42,875 --> 00:15:45,375
to secretly escort Prince Fa Yuanrong

319
00:15:45,791 --> 00:15:46,750
back to Liao to take the throne.

320
00:15:47,416 --> 00:15:48,291
The new ruler of Liao

321
00:15:48,375 --> 00:15:49,708
will never allow Fa Yuanrong to return.

322
00:15:50,041 --> 00:15:50,583
So,

323
00:15:50,666 --> 00:15:51,958
he will send assassins

324
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:53,333
to kill the Ninth Prince.

325
00:15:53,375 --> 00:15:55,375
That is why, for this mission,

326
00:15:56,041 --> 00:15:57,000
we will use the female Jinyiwei.

327
00:15:57,458 --> 00:16:00,208
It will draw less attention
and be safer.

328
00:16:00,208 --> 00:16:01,000
Exactly.

329
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:02,291
If the Northern Bureau

330
00:16:02,416 --> 00:16:04,083
mobilizes male Jinyiwei,
it will be too obvious.

331
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:10,541
Find the Ninth Prince, Fa Yuanrong,
as soon as possible.

332
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,333
Escort him back to Liao in secret

333
00:16:13,041 --> 00:16:14,125
and help him reclaim the throne.

334
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:15,791
Yes.

335
00:16:16,583 --> 00:16:18,208
We have to escort him back to Liao

336
00:16:18,375 --> 00:16:19,750
and help him take back the throne?

337
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:21,166
Didn't we agree

338
00:16:21,166 --> 00:16:22,583
we only had to get him to the border?

339
00:16:24,458 --> 00:16:25,375
The Commander's order

340
00:16:25,375 --> 00:16:26,916
is rather vague.

341
00:16:29,041 --> 00:16:29,666
Anyway,

342
00:16:29,916 --> 00:16:31,875
let's find this poor prince first.

343
00:16:32,541 --> 00:16:34,666
Xintian, go to the Imperial Academy.

344
00:16:34,666 --> 00:16:36,875
Bring the prince of Liao
to Chong'er Pavilion.

345
00:16:37,708 --> 00:16:38,416
Me?

346
00:16:38,875 --> 00:16:39,333
Yes.

347
00:16:39,541 --> 00:16:41,041
We need to plan the escort.

348
00:16:41,041 --> 00:16:42,125
You are the only one free.

349
00:16:42,458 --> 00:16:44,708
What assassin would dare

350
00:16:44,708 --> 00:16:46,041
make trouble in the capital
in broad daylight?

351
00:16:49,060 --> 00:16:50,640
(Imperial Academy)

352
00:16:54,583 --> 00:16:55,625
Hey.

353
00:16:56,125 --> 00:16:57,500
I'm a Jinyiwei from the Northern Bureau.

354
00:16:58,250 --> 00:16:59,375
Who are you looking for?

355
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,333
May I ask

356
00:17:00,333 --> 00:17:00,708
whether

357
00:17:00,708 --> 00:17:02,333
you have someone named Fa Yuanrong here?

358
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:04,166
Yuanrong?

359
00:17:05,041 --> 00:17:05,833
He is pulling weeds out back.

360
00:17:05,916 --> 00:17:07,458
Works hard too. Does it every day.

361
00:17:11,958 --> 00:17:12,416
Hey.

362
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,000
Are you Fa Yuanrong?

363
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,970
(Fa Yuanrong,
Ninth Prince of the Kingdom of Liao)

364
00:17:19,458 --> 00:17:20,166
Don't run!

365
00:17:20,208 --> 00:17:21,958
(Calling Card)
I'm a Jinyiwei from the Northern Bureau.

366
00:17:21,958 --> 00:17:22,708
(Calling Card)
This is the calling card.

367
00:17:22,708 --> 00:17:23,166
Jinyiwei?

368
00:17:24,125 --> 00:17:25,125
You are here to kill me, right?

369
00:17:25,375 --> 00:17:26,500
No! No one is here to kill you.

370
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:26,791
Who said...

371
00:17:28,208 --> 00:17:29,416
No one is trying to kill you.

372
00:17:29,708 --> 00:17:30,625
Stop!

373
00:17:45,458 --> 00:17:45,708
Hey!

374
00:17:46,125 --> 00:17:46,875
Come on!

375
00:17:47,375 --> 00:17:48,000
Stop!

376
00:17:50,291 --> 00:17:51,208
Stop!

377
00:17:51,625 --> 00:17:52,375
Coming through!

378
00:17:52,541 --> 00:17:53,458
Why are you running?

379
00:17:55,208 --> 00:17:56,083
Stop right there!

380
00:17:57,208 --> 00:17:57,750
What are you doing?

381
00:17:58,958 --> 00:17:59,458
Watch it!

382
00:17:59,458 --> 00:17:59,958
Stop!

383
00:18:00,083 --> 00:18:01,208
Stop!

384
00:18:01,416 --> 00:18:01,958
What is going on?

385
00:18:05,625 --> 00:18:06,333
Watch it!

386
00:18:07,250 --> 00:18:08,208
Come on!

387
00:18:09,333 --> 00:18:10,125
What happened?

388
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:10,958
What is going on?

389
00:18:11,125 --> 00:18:12,250
Why are you running like that?

390
00:18:12,583 --> 00:18:14,125
You knocked everything over.
Are you blind?

391
00:18:14,875 --> 00:18:15,625
Watch it!

392
00:18:17,083 --> 00:18:17,958
Hey!

393
00:18:18,041 --> 00:18:18,958
Stop!

394
00:18:19,208 --> 00:18:20,166
(Chong'er Pavilion)
Why is Xintian not back yet?

395
00:18:20,416 --> 00:18:21,416
(Chong'er Pavilion)
Let's ask Duoyu.

396
00:18:21,833 --> 00:18:23,000
(Chong'er Pavilion)
I hope nothing happened.

397
00:18:25,291 --> 00:18:25,750
Duoyu.

398
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:27,916
Hua. Bingfan.

399
00:18:28,416 --> 00:18:29,541
The Commander sent me to tell you.

400
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,083
Word is, assassins from Liao
have entered the capital.

401
00:18:32,375 --> 00:18:33,041
What?

402
00:18:48,770 --> 00:18:51,940
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

403
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:55,690
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

404
00:18:55,940 --> 00:18:58,940
♪My heart drifted lost♪

405
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:02,350
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

406
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:06,650
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

407
00:19:07,060 --> 00:19:10,400
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

408
00:19:10,980 --> 00:19:13,190
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

409
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:17,230
♪I've softly let it go♪

410
00:19:17,230 --> 00:19:21,100
♪The vow you made was true♪

411
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:24,850
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

412
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:27,060
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

413
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:31,600
♪And forget at world's end♪

414
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,400
♪Embracing memory♪

415
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:35,770
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

416
00:19:35,770 --> 00:19:39,650
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

417
00:19:39,650 --> 00:19:41,980
♪I wish to let it pass♪

418
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:46,980
♪And run toward this vast life♪
